Short: Scrambles proverbs for you to unscramble
Uploader: tcreyn@ix.netcom.com
Author: Ted Reynolds
Type: Game/think
Requires: 1.3 or better, 1 meg or better

This game takes some well known (?) proverbs and scrambles the letters, your
task is to unscramble them. You are given extra points if you can solve them
in a preset amount of time. Further details of game play can be found in the
instructions contained in the game itself.

