        *** INSTALLATION ***
Copy the hisoftbasic.library to your libs drawer.  Put all other files from
the archive in the directory you wish to run it from.  That's it, I hope you
have fun with my game.

        *** NOTE ***
Workbench 3.1 users may wish to use NoFastMem prior to starting the game.
For some reason hisoft basic does not exit gracefully under 3.1 and will
cause a system crash if fast memory is active.
